<L>__{exterior around the next corner. moments later}
<A>__{colin is waiting, in a doorway of his own. he has a knife open in his hand. he waits, listening to (faltering) footsteps: a man, face invisible in shadow, turns the corner. colin pulls him into the doorway and rips upwards with a knife. as the body falls we see: it isn't billy. it's a chinese man. colin backs away in horror, and hurries off down the street.}
